OL,3,CWaspi group: Safeguard will 'prevent
OL,4,Crisk of financial ruin' in
OL,5,Ccompensation bid
OL,7,FWaspi campaigners say they have
OL,8,Fsecured a vital legal safeguard in
OL,9,Ftheir bid for a High Court challenge.
OL,11,FThe Women Against State Pension
OL,12,FInequality (Waspi) group is seeking a
OL,13,Fjudicial review to force the
OL,14,FGovernment to reconsider its decision
OL,15,Fto rule out a compensation package for
OL,16,Fwomen affected by the way changes to
OL,17,Fthe state pension age were
OL,18,Fcommunicated.
