OL,3,CWaspi group: Safeguard will 'prevent
OL,4,Crisk of financial ruin' in
OL,5,Ccompensation bid
OL,7,FOn Monday, Waspi said a limit has been
OL,8,Fplaced on the campaign's liability for
OL,9,FDepartment for Work and Pensions (DWP)
OL,10,Fdefence costs.
OL,12,FWaspi said the DWP had agreed to a
OL,13,Fcosts capping order, protecting each
OL,14,Fside in the event they lose.
OL,16,FThe campaigners previously said they
OL,17,Fhad received an update to say that
OL,18,Ftheir case is arguable, setting them
OL,19,Fon course for a court hearing.
