OL,3,CWaspi group: Safeguard will 'prevent
OL,4,Crisk of financial ruin' in
OL,5,Ccompensation bid
OL,7,FA previous report by the Parliamentary
OL,8,Fand Health Service Ombudsman (PHSO)
OL,9,Fsuggested compensation ranging between
OL,10,F#1,000 and #2,950 could be appropriate
OL,11,Ffor each of those affected.
OL,13,FBut in December 2024, the Government
OL,14,Fsaid that, while it accepted the
OL,15,Fombudsman's finding of
OL,16,Fmaladministration and apologised for
OL,17,Fthere being a delay in writing to
OL,18,F1950s-born women, a blanket
OL,19,Fcompensation scheme, which could cost
OL,20,Ftaxpayers up to #10.5 billion, cannot
OL,21,Fbe justified.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
