OL,3,CWaspi group: Safeguard will 'prevent
OL,4,Crisk of financial ruin' in
OL,5,Ccompensation bid
OL,7,FCampaigners submitted arguments in
OL,8,FFebruary for a legal case challenging
OL,9,Fthe decision not to compensate women.
OL,11,FWaspi said the capping agreement
OL,12,Flimits its liability for Government
OL,13,Flegal costs to #60,000.
OL,15,FBut campaigners are continuing to ask
OL,16,Fsupporters to contribute to its legal
OL,17,F"fighting fund," saying they must
OL,18,Fraise enough to cover not only the
OL,19,Fcapped costs, but those of the legal
OL,20,Fteam fighting the case.
