OL,7,F"This is the fight of our lives"
OL,9,FAngela Madden from Derbyshire is the
OL,10,FChairwoman of Waspi, and said:
OL,11,F"Without this safeguard, we faced a
OL,12,Freal risk of financial ruin ` of
OL,13,Feffectively being silenced by the
OL,14,Fthreat of Government legal bills
OL,15,Frunning into hundreds of thousands of
OL,16,Fpounds.
OL,18,F"We now have the certainty we need to
OL,19,Fpress on ` but the costs of fighting
OL,20,Fthis case remain very real."
