OL,7,FShe added: "This is the fight of our
OL,8,Flives."
OL,10,FA DWP spokesperson said: "We do not
OL,11,Fcomment on live litigation.
OL,13,F"We have apologised for there being a
OL,14,F28-month delay in writing to 1950s-
OL,15,Fborn women.
OL,17,F"However, we do not agree with the
OL,18,Fombudsman's approach to injustice or
OL,19,Fremedy and that is why we have decided
OL,20,Fnot to pay compensation."
